Do using the much more current  [fr.opensagres.poi.xwpf.converter.pdf](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/fr.opensagres.xdocreport/fr.opensagres.poi.xwpf.converter.pdf/2.0.1), which works using the latest stable release `apache poi 3.17`.

